'''Kentucky Route 48''' ('''KY&nbsp;48''') is an {{convert|11|mi|km|adj=mid|-long}} [[state highway]] in the U.S. state of [[Kentucky]]. KY 48 runs from [[U.S. Route 31E]] (US 31E) and [[U.S. Route 150 in Kentucky|U.S. Route 150]] (US 150) in [[Highgrove, Kentucky|Highgrove]] to [[U.S. Route 62 in Kentucky|US 62]] and [[Kentucky Route 55|KY 55]] in [[Bloomfield, Kentucky|Bloomfield]], passing through the community of [[Fairfield, Kentucky|Fairfield]].

==Route description==
KY 48 travels southeast from US 31E in [[Nelson County, Kentucky|Nelson County]]. After about {{convert|1.5|mi|km}} southeast of Highgrove, KY 48 enters Spencer County and straddles the county line before reentering Nelson County west of Fairfield. After passing through Fairfield, KY 48 begins heading eastward before terminating at US 62 and KY 55 in Bloomfield.
{{-}}

